WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:07.340 --> 00:00:10.909
At the World Economic Forum on Africa 
in Dar es Salaam, Tanzania, 

00:00:10.909 --> 00:00:14.089
we are setting up a 
Davos Debates video corner. 

00:00:14.089 --> 00:00:18.500
Here, participants including 
presidents and business leaders 

00:00:18.500 --> 00:00:25.070
will respond via video to your questions and ideas 
on the region's most pressing challenges.

00:00:25.070 --> 00:00:32.380
So, what is your vision for Africa? And what 
opportunities and barriers does Africa face? 

00:00:32.380 --> 00:00:35.600
What questions do you have for the 
leaders who will gather in Dar es Salaam?

00:00:35.600 --> 00:00:38.320
Send your ideas and questions via 
video or text to YouTube.com/Davos. 

00:00:38.320 --> 00:00:43.890
You can also vote on your favourite contributions from others. 
The contributions with the highest number of votes 

00:00:43.890 --> 00:00:46.710
will be put to the leaders at 
the Davos Debates corner 

00:00:46.710 --> 00:00:51.340
giving you direct access to some of the most 
powerful and influential people in the world. 

00:00:51.340 --> 00:00:54.360
The best entries may also 
be shown at the meeting.

00:00:54.360 --> 00:00:55.639
Tell us what you think.

00:00:55.639 --> 00:00:59.159
Go to YouTube.com/Davos 
to join the conversation.

